{"tid":2398780,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香討：一國兩制是政治一國、經濟兩制","createTime":"2021-02-07T14:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T02:53:49.000Z","uid":201464,"like":17,"dislike":248,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"70bbf7909ba80431927b34b3d97ae92eafd8e866","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"香港當然還是一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治，只不過是去蕪存菁，把底線劃清楚罷了。<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制是政治一國、經濟兩制。想搞港獨自決的變相兩國兩制可以安息了。<br />\n<br />\n各級選舉的候選人仍舊需要有港人身份參與港人治港，但同時也需要擁護基本法及憲法的愛國者，離心離德者這份工閣下不合適。<br />\n<br />\n香港若能高度自治官民合作固然是好，但之譬如黑暴、老美欺上門來、疫症檢測、搶疫苗等力有不逮，you are not alone 祖國一定給你援手。<br />\n<br />\n或許有些人不認定，個人認為這是與時並進的進階版一國兩制2.0<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制已過時，要改"},{"pid":"580b3eac5e8e3d1f929bf482c3c210d34758c103","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":166,"dislike":0,"score":166,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"鄧小平：除國防和外交外。。。"},{"pid":"08407adb18ca1e864a2f1eb90f8d1ac894fb92c3","tid":2398780,"uid":71092,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"進階版一國兩制2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忽撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f626e348a602880da1043e97638cc8fa1601aea","tid":2398780,"uid":22609,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"到時經濟都一國埋佢哋又會點講呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩個制度都係一樣嘅 所以叫做兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a778ad3cd124d3c2b784af2447dd5d21af80f5","tid":2398780,"uid":191815,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"到時回血劍 又話經濟一國 馬路兩制<br />\n香港係左上右落 所以香港仲有兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c930123a75bdb520a4225ec00d29dcc41a3fd857","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"鄧小平：除國防、外交由中央人民政府管轄外，香港特別行政區享有行政管理權、立法權、獨立的司法權和終審權。"},{"pid":"b9d3f05dfaf026825914ab412cf60d3e676ce2e6","tid":2398780,"uid":37232,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"中共文宣好勁"},{"pid":"1f24f20bddff2d54b824cfcb4ce0b69e59c6e2db","tid":2398780,"uid":326665,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"我唔介意你呢個一國兩制嘅解釋，但可唔可以係1984年講清楚而唔係而家呢？"},{"pid":"da2780c66f5f277daecdcd210d05aa07a4b41c20","tid":2398780,"uid":301915,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"屌...佢鐘意點講米點講羅....可以係你制我唔制...又或者我制你唔制...總之地球第一鐵律 --- 誰大誰惡誰正確.....講鳩咩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8161060034a5ddc4a1073fcef80401c09086c9e3","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f24f20bddff2d54b824cfcb4ce0b69e59c6e2db","tid":2398780,"uid":326665,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"我唔介意你呢個一國兩制嘅解釋，但可唔可以係1984年講清楚而唔係而家呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"a269e19d045131c39a682a65c1ca5013fabc5a7e","tid":2398780,"uid":247892,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1f24f20bddff2d54b824cfcb4ce0b69e59c6e2db","tid":2398780,"uid":326665,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"我唔介意你呢個一國兩制嘅解釋，但可唔可以係1984年講清楚而唔係而家呢？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"當年大陸既掌權人都唔係咁諗野啦<br />\n係而家班撚樣懶醒"},{"pid":"51afdbd28453ed46596a2dedf7b755af514a300a","tid":2398780,"uid":56015,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"中國都違反咗聯合聲明啦，仲一咩國兩咩制？ 多餘"},{"pid":"37242a952d947cd4801b2b