if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff2eb0ee8853b886167828b21fe1714d6de353f","tid":2398780,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"咁好明顯上面定調咗<br />\n<br />\n要同西方講，唔係無咗一国兩制，而係一国兩制嘅進步版<br />\n<br />\n所以點解民建聯跳出嚟話&ldquo;變革香港&rdquo;"},{"pid":"349beffd71cd8ec872fe5eb613d6acc5fde21569","tid":2398780,"uid":387460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:52:39.000Z","msg":"香討咩都可以扭曲俾佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e2fe4c118c8f99c09428c7d52d1a0eef741f5","tid":2398780,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70bbf7909ba80431927b34b3d97ae92eafd8e866","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"香港當然還是一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治，只不過是去蕪存菁，把底線劃清楚罷了。<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制是政治一國、經濟兩制。想搞港獨自決的變相兩國兩制可以安息了。<br />\n<br />\n各級選舉的候選人仍舊需要有港人身份參與港人治港，但同時也需要擁護基本法及憲法的愛國者，離心離德者這份工閣下不合適。<br />\n<br />\n香港若能高度自治官民合作固然是好，但之譬如黑暴、老美欺上門來、疫症檢測、搶疫苗等力有不逮，you are not alone 祖國一定給你援手。<br />\n<br />\n或許有些人不認定，個人認為這是與時並進的進階版一國兩制2.0<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制已過時，要改"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"藍C有讀書唔駛咁撚豬，佢地只係認錢錢錢利益利益利益"},{"pid":"474c9d37c008010f8071592e3576aac992090e95","tid":2398780,"uid":372384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f24f20bddff2d54b824cfcb4ce0b69e59c6e2db","tid":2398780,"uid":326665,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"我唔介意你呢個一國兩制嘅解釋，但可唔可以係1984年講清楚而唔係而家呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"唔講清楚佢先至有餘地亂咁加"},{"pid":"b86fd8f77babca56dae7b3d62fcb46f1535e4fd2","tid":2398780,"uid":62935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"什么经济两制？<br />\n<br />\n既是一国，就是国家为主，习主席为首。<br />\n<br />\n疫症当前，国家经济有重担，连海航等国企都有危难，还要搞经济分家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我看什么香港讨论区？是大旗大鼓搞分裂吗？<br />\n<br />\n你那有见过啥北京讨论区、广东讨论区、新疆讨论区、蒙古讨论区？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是反动分子的营地吗？<br />\n<br />\n同志們，要不咱明天看看跟国安举报一下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce37f4cc676e5a2be84ebf0b3758807af360864","tid":2398780,"uid":164509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3888dc9ee00a47672b93943ab650dfbc470c7c12","tid":2398780,"uid":279298,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"中國是個奇妙的國家，一群社會底層的人明明被壓榨著，卻擁有上位者的思考方法，處處為當權者著想"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:59:15.000Z","msg":"係動物世界搵唔到呢種蠢貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6339b7a202fd42a3a40caedf3194ca58d4786223","tid":2398780,"uid":288699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3888dc9ee00a47672b93943ab650dfbc470c7c12","tid":2398780,"uid":279298,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"中國是個奇妙的國家，一群社會底層的人明明被壓榨著，卻擁有上位者的思考方法，處處為當權者著想"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"奴隸都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c33c6bf12225b5fd883b96ef063873b89ae60e3","tid":2398780,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:04:09.000Z","msg":"鄧小平：Am i a joke to you?"},{"pid":"ef5856c257a2f001d1803513b89a7b5463d03d27","tid":2398780,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7d868ddccfb5d93104fa62d600b6787e71436e","tid":2398780,"uid":321859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"香討釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e8eefdf66c82c8debf062b8ddd7b6